# data

**Instance Property**

The feature print data.

## Declaration

```swift
var data: Data { get }
```

## Discussion

The data is divided into separate elements. Determine the type of element using [doc://Vision/documentation/Vision/VNFeaturePrintObservation/elementType], and the number of elements using [doc://Vision/documentation/Vision/VNFeaturePrintObservation/elementCount].

## Fetching Feature Print Data

- **elementCount**: The total number of elements in the data.
